      "raw_text": "The wreck of the Northern Pacific\neastbound train, No. 4. in the YakI-\nma canyon, is reported cleared up and\nNo. is due in Spokane at 4 o'clock\nthis afternoon. Express Messenger\nAdams. who was hurt in this wreck,\nis reported in n serious condition. No\none else was injured.\n\n\nThe wreck was due to defective\nfish car The engine, two refriger-\nator, mail and express cars were de-\nrallied. A new train was made up in\nSpokane and sent east."
